L-egume 1.4
--------------------
- Version compatible with python 3 (tested 3.9), win10 64bit and linux
- Add new plant compartments (aerien_nonrec, reserve), both for C (dry matter) and N
- Update plant fluxes to the soil from the different compartments
- Update StartEach / EndEach function for  external coupling (option: opt_external_coupling) and provide examples
- remove VGL submodules riri5 and soil3ds from the l-egume distribution (have now separated distributions and installations)
- change input files for running simulations with more than 2 species (exemple_ls_plt.xls file)
- improve features for detailed leaf visualisation (opt_Trud, noiseGeom)



L-egume 1.3
--------------------
- Version compatible with python 3 (tested 3.9), win10 64bit and linux
- New version including intra-population variability (opt_sd)
- Add run_legume_usm.py to easily lauch the model from command line and distant servers (singularity container / Docker)
- Correction of Temperature response calculation and introduction of the optGel and optPP options -> Udev concept to drive the model 
- improved features to visualize model outputs (individual variability...)


L-egume 1.2
--------------------
- Version compatible with python 3 (tested 3.7), win10 64bit
- beta version compatible for vgl-grass
- new features to visualize model outputs (soil profile, color gradients for plant features...)


L-egume 1.1
--------------------

First updated version of L-egume 
-remove R dependencies of the model 
-compatible win64 / linux
-add non-regression tests



L-egume 1.0
--------------------

First version of L-egume.
